    <h1><u>Paid Tours and Museums!</u><h1>
      <h3>Countless historic landmarks and monuments like the Boston Tea Party or even the oldest ballpark in history are located in the city of Boston! Therefore, there are many great tours and museums that will inform the public about Boston! On the other hand Boston is home to some of the finest Museums in the country! A trip to Boston in incomplete without visiting one of the these places!<h3>
        
