              <h1>Fenway Park Tour</h1>
              <h3>If you were unaware Fenway Park is full of rich history like the red chair or the morse code hidden on the scoreboard! If you are a fan of the Red Sox we would highly recommend visiting the Fenway Park tour! The cost of the tour is not too expensive. The tour lasts about one hour and it is incredibly fascinating. If you are lucky you will be able to walk on the field but a protip is to not go on the tour on game day because you will not be able to visit all of the attractions because they will be preparing for the game! This tour is great fun and we would recommend this tour to all baseball fans!<h3>
       
