     <h1>Museum of Science<h1>
       <h3>The Museum of Science does a great job making learning about science incredibly fun! Unlike most museums, the 
Museum of Science is essentially a bunch of labs that kids can do to learn about science! Plus, there are a bunch of other fun things like movies, energy shows lectures and even a roller coaster! I would highly recommend the Museum of Science for young kids and their parents! New exhibits and documentaries and movies are added to the museum all the time so there is always something new to do at the museum! 
The Museum of Science is a little bit expensive but it is a lot of fun! Some of our favorite memories were made in the Museum of Science. The Museum of Science is a great way to spend your weekends. In Fact, billionaire Michael Bloomberg, donated 50 million dollars to the Museum of Science because that's where he learned a lot about science! 
